            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I am a student iys a academic school it focuses on  students health behavior\nAnd make them a good and loving child\nAs a student when you go to 5th they train you for 6th as in 6th class the school starts from 7 to 2\nRegards VIDHU FROM 5 TULIP\nTHRUSDAY 22 JUNE 2023",
          "publisher": {
